<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100713421.jpg" alt="1758100713421.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100713421.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">9月12日上午，新生体检点各功能区域规范划分、标识清晰，新生们怀着对自身健康的重视，遵循现场指引有序排队、逐项参与入学检查。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">医护人员专注操作、耐心答疑，志愿者穿梭其间提供引导与协助，整场体检流程高效又顺畅。经济管理学院学工办主任郭伟也来到现场，查看体检进展，与医护人员沟通细节，并不时叮嘱新生注意检查流程，用细致关怀为新生健康“护航”。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">新生们有序排队，依次进行视力检查。医护人员耐心指引大家用手轻轻遮盖单眼，仔细辨认视标字符，并同步认真记录下视力检测结果。 </span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100738866.jpg" alt="1758100738866.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100738866.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100752301.jpg" alt="1758100752301.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100752301.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100773522.jpg" alt="1758100773522.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100773522.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">检查台前，医生细致查看牙齿、牙龈状况，排查龋齿、评估牙龈健康。让新生既了解自身状况，也掌握实用护理技巧。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100784522.jpg" alt="1758100784522.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100784522.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100803305.jpg" alt="1758100803305.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100803305.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">志愿者为新生检测口腔情况</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">面对抽血，部分新生略显紧张，医护人员娴熟操作，志愿者及时递上棉签并轻声安抚。从血常规到传染病筛查，每份样本都为健康评估和校园集体健康提供依据。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100863247.jpg" alt="1758100863247.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100863247.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100890506.jpg" alt="1758100890506.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100890506.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100899946.jpg" alt="1758100899946.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100899946.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">医护人员为新生采血</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">另外特别协调移动放射车停靠于体检场地外，车上医护人员为新生做胸部检查，避免了新生们四处奔波，也让体检过程变得更加完整，健康评估更加全面。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100958212.jpg" alt="1758100958212.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100958212.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100975001.jpg" alt="1758100975001.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758100975001.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">新生们排队上车做检查</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">新生依次站上体重秤，医护人员快速记录体重数值；随后转身背靠身高尺，头顶对齐刻度线，读取身高数据。两项基础指标为后续军训中调整训练强度、保障体能适配提供参考，让健康评估从“量”开始，扎实又清晰。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758101031937.jpg" alt="1758101031937.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758101031937.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">从视力筛查到心肺检查，从抽血化验到身高体重测量，这场新生体检是对身体状况的全面“摸底”。每一项检查、每一组数据，都藏着对新生顺利开启校园生活的用心。待所有结果尘埃落定，大家带着健康底气，在阳光下继续热血军训，为大学生活写下活力满满的第一页。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758101054421.jpg" alt="1758101054421.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1758101054421.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p>